DE_Dust_13_Beta1

Map by Android X

Install instructions:
Just copy "de_dust_13_beta1.bsp" to the "maps" folder located were you installed counter strike source.

    Uses standard textures.

    The basic structure of the map is set out but there is a lot more detail to go into this map. Suggestions on how
        to make this map better are welcome.

    Please report any suggestions or bugs in this map to rowdyshadowfire@yahoo.com.au
